title: Doctor Who - Big Finish - Dalek Empire series
description:
"Dalek Empire" made by Big Finish
is a collection of four Doctor Who audio stories,
plus a Doctor Who spin-off audio series of 18 episodes,
about Mankind fighting the Dalek invasion of their galaxy.


Contains:
- From the main Doctor Who audio series:
"The Genocide Machine" with the 7th Doctor and Ace
"The Apocalypse Element" with the 6th Doctor, Evelyn and Romana
"The Mutant Phase" with the 5th Doctor and Nyssa
"The Time of the Daleks" with the 8th Doctor and Charley

- The "Dalek Empire" spin-off series itself:
Seasons 1 and 2 about the Dalek invasion in the 42nd century
Season 3 about a second invasion 2500 years later
Season 4 returns to the first invasion with different characters



If your media player can't read .m4a try changing the extension to .m4b
If it still doesn't work, update codecs or change player.
